title: KATE BUSH LIVE IN CONCERT 1979 [Remastered] DVD-R
description:
KATE BUSH, LIVE AT THE HAMMERSMITH ODEON 1979 Remastered edition [DVDR]

Kate Bush's one and only live visual release restored and remastered for DVD, complete with bonus materials including the Tour Programme, a gallery of over 100 images plus the 'On Stage' EP. With animated menu and full artwork this is one for the fans.

SONGS PERFORMED
Moving, Them Heavy People, Violin, Strange Phenomena, Hammer Horror, Don't Push Your Foot On The Heartbrake, Wow, Feel It, Kite, James & The Cold Gun, Oh England My Lionheart, Wuthering Heights.

BONUS FEATURES
- Restoration trailer.
- Animated menu and photo gallery with tour program & 100+ photos.
- On Stage audio EP recorded at the Hammersmith Odeon 5/13/79
Them Heavy People, Don't Push Your Foot On The Heartbrake, James and The Cold Gun, L'Amour Looks Something Like You.
